model
Class Move

java.lang.Object
  model.Move

public class Move
extends java.lang.Object

The Move class is an immutable class. The Move class represents different moves that a player may make during a game of antichess. Any moves constructed are not necessarily allowed by the rules of antichess, and must be validated before they can be applied to a Board.

Specification Fields
  • from : Square //the Square that the Piece being move resides at
  • to : Square //the Square that the Piece being moved will move to
  • path : Set //the Squares that the Piece must travel over
  • distance : int //the total distance the Piece must travel

(m.to = to) &&
